Youâ€™ve heard how South Bend, Indiana, Mayor Pete Buttigieg is coming on strong in Iowa. Youâ€™ve heard how New Hampshire is a free-for-all. And youâ€™ve heard about former Vice President Joe Bidenâ€™s firewall in Nevada and especially South Carolina.
