To be sure, we donâ€™t know how the impeachment saga will unfold, but the electoral ramifications on the GOP side are something to keep in mind. Thatâ€™s because even if there is some movement in a pro-impeachment direction among Republican voters, there may still be some senators up in 2020 who fear the potential dangers of angering the party base and getting a serious primary challenge.
