Fox News has discussed Hunter Bidenâ€™s ties to a gas company in Ukraine â€” as well his ties to China â€” more than the other outlets. It frequently mentioned â€œHillary Clinton,â€ and the idea that she, too, might have shadowy connections to Ukraine. Fox also used the phrase â€œquid pro quoâ€ more often than the other networks, with most coverage pointing out that Trump did not explicitly ask for a â€œquid pro quoâ€ or promise Zelensky foreign assistance for Ukrainian cooperation.
