Race rating is the median rating from Inside Elections, Sabatoâ€™s Crystal Ball and The Cook Political Report. Some candidatesâ€™ second-quarter reports did not appear on the FEC site as of noon on Tuesday, July 16, so data may be incomplete. In New Hampshire, no Republican candidate had filed to challenge incumbent Sen. Jeanne Shaheen by the time the books closed on the second quarter.
*Includes $46,451 raised by incumbent Sen. Tom Udall, who will not seek reelection.
