With just a few hours to go before the voting starts in Iowa, itâ€™s time for us to freeze the FiveThirtyEight primary forecast model! So here are our final estimates of each candidateâ€™s chance of winning a majority of pledged delegates and their chances of winning Iowa ahead of tonightâ€™s vote.
